parameters.name: withProperties

method.name: count
method.shortdesc: Displays the number of elements in the PreflightProfile.

method.name: item
method.shortdesc: Returns the PreflightProfile with the specified index or name.

parameters.name: index

method.name: itemByName

method.name: itemByID
method.shortdesc: Returns the PreflightProfile with the specified ID.

method.name: itemByRange
method.shortdesc: Returns the PreflightProfiles within the specified range.

parameters.name: from
parameters.shortdesc: The PreflightProfile, index, or name at the beginning of the range. Can accept: PreflightProfile, Long Integer or String.

parameters.name: to
parameters.shortdesc: The PreflightProfile, index, or name at the end of the range. Can accept: PreflightProfile, Long Integer or String.

method.name: firstItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the first PreflightProfile in the collection.

method.name: lastItem

method.name: previousItem
method.shortdesc: Returns the PreflightProfile with the index previous to the specified index.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.shortdesc: The index of the PreflightProfile that follows the desired PreflightProfile.

parameters.name: obj
parameters.shortdesc: The PreflightProfile whose index comes before the desired PreflightProfile.

method.shortdesc: Returns any PreflightProfile in the collection.

method.name: everyItem
method.shortdesc: Returns every PreflightProfile in the collection.
